Former Champion Raikkonen Returns to Formula One With Renault

-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 
2011-11-29T08:11:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/former-champion-raikkonen-returns-to-formula-one-with-renault.html
Former Formula One champion Kimi
Raikkonen agreed to drive for the Lotus Renault team next
season, returning to the series after two years in the World
Rally Championship.  Raikkonen, 32, agreed to a two-year contract, the Enstone,
England-based team said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  